title: 05/12/21 DPS Hour 2 Pat Forde and Mike Florio
itunes:title: 05/12/21 DPS Hour 2 Pat Forde and Mike Florio
description:
Pat Forde talks about Medina Spirit being allowed to run in the Preakness. Pat says that he is not surprised that Medina Spirit will get to run in the Preakness. Mike Florio says that the Tim Tebow signing is nothing other than a side show. Mike says that it is going to happen, the question is; when will it happen?
